From: Lulu Cheng <chenglulu@loongson.cn>
Date: Tue, 19 Nov 2024 19:35:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] LoongArch: Set the default code model to medium.

gcc/ChangeLog:

	* config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc: Do.
---
 gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc b/gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc
index 8408a70e5ca..40a2955c502 100644
--- a/gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc
+++ b/gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch-opts.cc
@@ -540,7 +540,7 @@ fallback:
 
 
   /* 5.  Target code model */
-  t.cmodel = constrained.cmodel ? target->cmodel : CMODEL_NORMAL;
+  t.cmodel = constrained.cmodel ? target->cmodel : CMODEL_MEDIUM;
 
   switch (t.cmodel)
     {
